# Rexel Elektra Design System — Cursor Rules

> Source: Figma Design System Library (Elektra)
> Default theme: Rexel Group
> Multi-brand: supports 11 brands via token aliasing

---

## Fonts

- **Headings & Display**: Montserrat (SemiBold)
- **Body, Labels, Links, Prices**: Open Sans (Regular, SemiBold, Bold)
- **Icons**: Font Awesome 5 Free (Solid & Regular)

Import from Google Fonts:
```html
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;600;700&family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
```

