## Components — Detailed Specs

---

### Button
- **Types**: Primary, Secondary, Tertiary, Danger, OnSurface
- **Sizes**: Small, Medium, Large
- **States**: Default, Hover, Focus, Disabled, Loading, Success
- **Icons**: No icon, Leading icon, Trailing icon
- **Text**: Open Sans SemiBold 14px/20px
- **Border-radius**: 4px
- **Padding**: 8px 16px (Medium)

| Variant | Background | Text color | Border |
|---|---|---|---|
| Primary | #2E4EAA | #FFFFFF | none |
| Secondary | #FFFFFF | #2E4EAA | 1px solid #2E4EAA |
| Tertiary | transparent | #2E4EAA | none |
| Danger | #DA1E28 | #FFFFFF | none |
| OnSurface | #FFFFFF | text-primary | 1px solid border-subtle |
| Disabled | #E0E0E0 | #6F6F6F | none |

Loading state: replace label with spinner animation.
Success state: replace label with checkmark icon.

---

### Button Icon (icon-only)
- **Types**: Primary, Secondary, Tertiary, OnSurface
- **Sizes**: Small (30px), Medium (36px), Large (43px)
- **Forms**: Square (border-radius 4px), Circle (border-radius 50%)
- **States**: Default, Hover, Active, Disabled
- Same color logic as Button

---

### Round Button
- **Sizes**: Small (30px), Normal (36px), Large (43px)
- **States**: Default, Hover, Focus, Disabled
- Circular shape, used for add-to-cart and icon actions

---

### Button Add to Cart (animated)
- **Types**: Primary, Secondary
- **States**: Default, Hover, Focus, Disabled, Loading, Loading-anim, Success, Fail
- Icon: cart icon (Font Awesome)
- Animated transition: Default → Loading spinner → Success checkmark (or Fail warning)

---

### Inline Alerts
- **Types**: Global alert (full width, top of page), Content alert (inline in content)
- **Styles**: Default (with description + link), Compact (single line)
- **Messages**: Default (blue), Information (blue), Success (green), Warning (orange), Critical (red)

| Message | Background | Border-left | Icon color | Text color |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Information | Blue/10 #EDF5FF | 3px solid Blue/60 #0F62FE | Blue/60 | text-primary |
| Success | Green/10 #DEFBE6 | 3px solid Green/60 #198038 | Green/60 | text-primary |
| Warning | Orange/10 #FFF2E8 | 3px solid Orange/60 #BA4E00 | Orange/60 | text-primary |
| Critical | Red/10 #FFF1F1 | 3px solid Red/60 #DA1E28 | Red/60 | text-primary |

Structure: Icon (left) + Title (Open Sans SemiBold 14px) + Description (Open Sans Regular 14px) + Optional link + Close button (×)
Compact variant: Icon + single line message, no description
Border-radius: 0 (sharp edges)
Padding: 16px

---

### Field (wrapper component)
- **Types**: Text, Dropdown, Multi Select, Text Area, Date Picker, Search, Password, Phone, Slot (custom)
- Wraps input components with: Label (top) + Input + Helper text (bottom) + Error message
- Label: Open Sans Regular 12px/18px, color text-secondary
- Helper text: Open Sans Regular 12px, color text-helper (#596179)
- Error text: Open Sans Regular 12px, color Red/60 (#DA1E28)

---

### Input Text
- **States**: Default, Hover, Focus, Active, Disabled, Read Only, Error, Success
- **Filled**: Yes / No (empty placeholder)
- Border default: 1px solid border-subtle (#D7D9E4)
- Border hover: 1px solid border-strong (#9FA4B7)
- Border focus: 2px solid border-brand (#2E4EAA)
- Border error: 1px solid Red/60 (#DA1E28)
- Border success: 1px solid Green/60 (#198038)
- Background: #FFFFFF (default), #F4F4F4 (disabled/read only)
- Text: Open Sans Regular 14px/20px, color text-primary
- Placeholder: Open Sans Regular 14px/20px, color text-placeholder (#A8A8A8)
- Border-radius: 4px
- Height: 40px
- Padding: 0 16px

---

### Input Password
- Same as Input Text + visibility toggle icon (eye/eye-off)
- States: Default, Hover, Focus, Active, Read Only, Error, Success
- Toggle: show/hide password (Font Awesome eye icon)

---

### Input Phone
- Same as Input Text + country prefix dropdown on the left
- States: Default, Read Only, Error, Success, Hover, Focus Prefix, Focus Field, Focus Dropdown, Active

---

### Text Area
- **States**: Default, Hover, Focus, Active, Disabled, Read Only, Error
- Same styling as Input Text but multi-line
- Resizable vertically
- Min-height: 80px

---

### Dropdown / Select
- **States**: Default, Hover, Focus, Active, Disabled, Error, Read Only
- **Filled**: Yes / No
- Same border/styling as Input Text
- Chevron icon (Font Awesome) on the right side
- Dropdown menu: white background, 1px solid border-subtle, box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)
- Menu items: Open Sans Regular 14px/20px, hover background layer-01 (#F3F3FA)

---

### Multi Select
- Dropdown with checkboxes
- Selected items shown as pills/chips inside the field
- Same container styling as Dropdown

---

### Date Picker
- **States**: Default, Focus, Active, Disabled, Error, Read Only, Value in, Error value in
- **Calendar types**: Single date, Period (range selection)
- Input field: same styling as Input Text + calendar icon
- Calendar popup: white background, border-subtle, days in grid
- Day states: Not selected, Hover, Selected (background brand), Period selected (background Primary/10), Disabled

---

### Checkbox
- **States**: Enabled, Selected, Partially selected, Disabled, Error
- **Focus**: Yes / No (focus ring: 2px solid border-brand)
- Checked: fill Primary/70 (#2E4EAA), white checkmark
- Partially selected: fill Primary/70, white dash
- Size: 18×18px
- Label: Open Sans Regular 14px/20px, gap 8px from checkbox

---

### Accordion
- **Open state**: Yes / No
- **UI variants**: Transparent (no background), On Color (grey background), Brand (brand background)
- **States**: Default, Hover
- Header: Open Sans SemiBold 14px/20px + chevron icon (rotates on open)
- Content area: padding 16px
- Border-bottom: 1px solid border-subtle

---

### Breadcrumb
- **Display**: Full, Overflow (truncated with "..."), Loading (skeleton)
- Items: Open Sans Regular 14px, color text-interactive (#2E4EAA)
- Current page: Open Sans Regular 14px, color text-primary (not clickable)
- Separator: "/" or chevron icon, color text-helper
- Item states: Default, Hover (underline), Focus

---

### Link
- **Types**: Primary (brand color), Secondary (grey), OnColor (white for dark backgrounds)
- **States**: Default, Hover, Focus, Visited
- Font: Open Sans SemiBold 14px (or 12px small, 16px large)
- Primary color: text-interactive (#2E4EAA)
- Underline: on hover
- Optional trailing icon (external link, arrow, etc.)

---

### Badge
- **Types**: Default, Already bought, Refurbished, Offer, Price flag, Loyalty, Criteria, Stock status (in stock / available J+X / not in stock)
- **Sizes**: Small, Medium, Large
- Small text labels, rounded pill shape
- Each type has its own color (green for stock, orange for offer, etc.)

---

### Product Card (PERSE)
- **Breakpoints**: XXL Grid (327px wide), Medium Grid (240px), Small/X-small (375px full width), List view (980px)
- **Status**: Default, Unavailable product
- **User status**: Logged-in (shows price + add to cart), Anonymous (no price)
- Structure: Product image (top) + Badge(s) + Product name (H4) + Reference + Price (Open Sans SemiBold) + Incremental Counter + Add to cart button
- Overlay variant: Product detail quick view, Mobile add to cart
- Border: 1px solid border-subtle, border-radius 8px

---

### Product Mini Card
- **States**: Default, 3 Ref vertical, My price, Was price, Anonymous
- Compact horizontal layout: thumbnail (left) + product info (right)
- Width: ~386px, Height: ~117px

---

### Product Recommendation Card
- **Types**: NBO (Next Best Offer), Recommendation, Recommendation-Special
- **Styles**: Light (white background), Dark (dark background)
- **Overlay**: None, Stocks (stock details overlay)
- Size: ~298×400px

---

### Option Cards
- **Types**: Radio button, Checkbox
- **Selection state**: Selected, Not selected
- **States**: Default, Hover, Focus, Disabled
- Selected: border 2px solid border-brand (#2E4EAA), subtle brand background
- Not selected: border 1px solid border-subtle (#D7D9E4)
- Size: ~232×146px

---

### Classic Card
- **Types**: Regular (vertical), Horizontal, Collapsable (open/closed)
- Structure: Image slot + Title (H3) + Description + CTA buttons
- Border: 1px solid border-subtle, border-radius 8px
- Background: white, padding 16px

---

### Incremental Counter (Quantity)
- **Sizes**: Small, Medium, Large
- **States**: Disabled, Filled, Focus Input, Focus Minus, Focus Plus, Read Only
- Structure: Minus button [-] + Number input + Plus button [+]
- Buttons: same styling as Button Icon Secondary
- Input: centered number, Open Sans SemiBold 14px

---

### Price
- **Versions**: MVP, To be dev later
- Font: Open Sans SemiBold
- Sizes: Extra Large (18px), Large (16px), Medium (14px), Small (12px), Superscript (10px)
- Structure: main price + optional unit (e.g. "/m") + optional crossed-out old price
- Superscript: used for decimal digits, smaller and raised

---

### Pagination
- Page numbers + Previous/Next arrows
- Active page: background brand (#2E4EAA), white text
- Inactive: no background, text-primary
- Hover: background layer-01
- Size: 36×36px per page button

---

### Pills / Chips
- Selectable filter tags
- States: Selected (brand background or brand border), Not selected (border-subtle)
- Border-radius: 16px (pill shape)
- Text: Open Sans Regular 14px
- Optional close icon (×)

---

### Tag
- Non-interactive labels
- Small: Open Sans Regular 12px
- Colors: various depending on type (status, category, etc.)
- Border-radius: 4px

---

### Carousel
- Image/content slider with navigation dots
- Controls: Previous/Next arrow buttons (Round Button)
- Position indicator: dots or numeric (e.g. "2/5")
- Play/Pause toggle for auto-scroll

---

### Loaders
- **Skeleton loader**: Rectangle or Rounded placeholder, animated shimmer, background Neutral/20
- **Spinner oval**: 48×48px, animated rotation
- **Spinner tail chasing**: 48×48px, alternative spinner style

---

### Stepper / Track & Trace (Post-Order)
- Progress indicator for multi-step flows (order tracking)
- Steps connected by line
- Completed step: brand color, checkmark icon
- Current step: brand color, filled circle
- Upcoming step: grey, empty circle

---

### Notification (animated)
- Small pulsing dot: 18×18px
- 4-step animation cycle
- Used on icons (cart, bell) to indicate new content

