## Multi-Brand Support

The Design System supports 11 brands through token aliasing:
Rexel Group, Rexel France, Regro, Schaecke, LearSmith, JohnTurk, Ideal, Nedco, Westburne, Atlantic, Sofinther

Each brand overrides the Primary and Grey color scales while keeping the same token names. When building prototypes, use the **Rexel Group** theme as default.

---

## Design Principles

1. Always use semantic tokens (e.g., `button-primary`, `text-secondary`) rather than raw hex values
2. Spacing follows the 4-8-16-24-32 scale — never use arbitrary values
3. Typography uses only Montserrat (headings) and Open Sans (everything else)
4. Icons are Font Awesome 5 — use the same icon set across all prototypes
5. Border-radius: 4px for interactive elements (buttons, inputs), 8px for containers (cards, modals)
6. Always provide visual feedback for interactive states (hover, focus, active, disabled)

